D

databaseTimeZone() - Method in class io.dropwizard.jdbi.DBIFactory
Get a time zone of a database Override this method to specify a time zone of a database to use in JodaDateTimeMapper and JodaDateTimeArgument It's needed for cases when the database operates in a different time zone then the application and it doesn't use the SQL type `TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE`.
